      "n": 28,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un skattijahs prett Sodo-\nnu un Gomorru / un prett wiſſu\nſkaju Semmi / un redſeja / un\nraugi / Duhmi zehſahs no tahs\nSemmes / itt ka kahda Zepta\nDuhmi."
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notikſe/kad DEews\ncht Klajuma Pilsfahtus fainai-\naja/ bij DEews Ahbraamna pehz\ntgahdajes/ un iſweddis to Lat-\nu no tahs Samaitafchanaſ Wid-\nuß/ kad winſch tohs Pilsfahtus\namitaja / furroß Lats mitte."
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un Lats gabje us augſchu\no Joaras/ un mitte Kalna Wir-\ni / un winna diwi Meitas ar\nixan/ jo winſch bibhajahs Joara\niſt/ un palikſe tur kahda Bedre\nhds ar fawahn diwi Meitahin."
    },
    {
      "n": 31,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija ta pirmdsim-\nufi us to jaunafu : Muhsu\nehws irr wezzigs / un Ziliveka\nwa wirs Seines/ kas pee mums\narr eet pehz wiſſas Paſaules\neradduma."
    },
    {
      "n": 32,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Mahz / lai mehs muhfu\nehwam Wihnu dohdam dſert/\npee ta gullam / un dsihwu\nfiummu no muhfu Tehwa\nturram."
    },
    {
      "n": 33,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee deive fawam Teh-\nam tanni Nakti Wihnu dſert/\nta pirmdsimmuſi nahze / un\nſleja pee fawa Tehwa / un\nwiſch ne nomannija to/ kad win-\napgullahs / nedſ kad winna\nlahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 34,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un no Rihta fazzija ta\nmdsimmuſi us to jaunafu :\nugi/es efmu Waktar Nakt pee"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "manna Tehwa gulſejuff/ lai mehs\nwinnam arridsan scho NaktiWih-\nnu dſert dohdam / tad ee-eij tu/un\ngulli pee ta/ ka mehs Dsimmuſu\ndsihwu paturram no muhfu\nTehwa."
    },
    {
      "n": 35,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tahs deive arridsan tan-\nni Nakti fawam Tehwam Wih-\nnu dſert / un ta jaunaka zehſahs/\nun gulſeja pee ta / un tas ne no-\nmannija kad winna apgullahs /\nnedſ kad winna zehſahs."
    },
    {
      "n": 36,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Latta diwi Meitas tap-\npe genhtas no fawa Tehwa."
    },
    {
      "n": 37,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta pirmdsimmuſi dſem-\ndeja weenn Dehlu / un noſauze\nwinna Wahrdü Moab / fchis irr\nto Moabitenu Tehws / lihds fchai\nDeenai."
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ta jaunaka dſemdeja\narri weenn Dehlu / un noſauze\nwinna Wahrdü Ben-Aimmi /\nfchis irr to Ammona Behrnu\nTehws/lihds fchai Deenai."
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "N Ahbraams aisgahje\nno turrenes / uhs to\nSemmi prett Deenas\nWidduspuffi / un mitte ſarp\nKahdes un ſarp Sur / un bija\nweens Sweſchineeks Gerara."
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Ahbraams fazzija no\nSaras fawas Geewas / ta irr\nmanna Mahsa / tad fuhtija Abi-\nE\nmeleks"
